<div class="com-share" data-id="17960" data-title="《Adele 唱片卖出去了，但唱片行业的好时光不会再回来》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/17960/medium/17960.jpg?1448277428" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/17960.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
